Awesome pictures Dave. I love this time of year.
Lamprey shot is the best if them all! Once again, great shots!
catch fish like no ones watchin

I like it Dave  Really digging the lamprey shot! I still haven't figured out a system that doesn't require taking dozens of pictures of failed attempts.  One shot I've always wanted to take is a head on shot (or close to) of a fish jumping directly at the camera. My friends in Alaska got close but they were chased off the river by hungry brown bears.LOL
